{"tid":134003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁國雄收逾二萬「公民提名」未達標　決定不參選特首","createTime":"2017-02-25T06:29:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T12:44:22.000Z","uid":48093,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7783ed9cbabb4004c63306506e835a3345b8d16d","tid":134003,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T06:29:22.000Z","msg":"社民連立法會議員梁國雄，早前表示如果收集到3萬8千個「公民提名」，便會參選行政長官。梁國雄在2星期內，於網上及街頭一共收到20234個「公民提名」，未達目標，他決定不會參選，結束收集「提名」。<br />\n<br />\n梁國雄表示，感謝市民支持，指「提名」的人願留下聯絡方法及身份證號碼，是對他的信任。他又指坊間有意見認為，有曾俊華參選便足夠，批評他鎅票，團隊爭取提名時會受到責備，他感謝團隊在壓力下仍然到街頭為他爭取「提名」。"},{"pid":"f6e53b0a03f2144f0605083e251c51e345036697","tid":134003,"uid":10295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T06:30:34.000Z","msg":"抵撚死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8bdad8b4cb9c60ea7b1328b895011774d0cbc1e","tid":134003,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T06:31:14.000Z","msg":"夠民主未？<br />\n<br />\n條氣順未？"},{"pid":"7fb7c56e5c18c34936c4df882899cb41121fe837","tid":134003,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T06:32:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5852056aac8a413e371f8debe5346da86d1ce59d","tid":134003,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T12:20:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好柒"},{"pid":"355694ee95fbe0ddbe934dc0b229fefb73f59a25","tid":134003,"uid":55077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T12:31:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">喂，阿哥!唔係咁就退出呀</span>"},{"pid":"7a30cc9a2b5b7e2463a0fdd39eed783228a33be0","tid":134003,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0